channel.title: Model header help
channel.description:
I used a model header i have found *not k4rn4ges bcuz his links no longer work* well now all my chaotics DC me when you try to look at them. Like if you spawn them u immediatly DC (just like having 634 models without a 634 model header) Oh and everything that was black before the model header is now transparent. Does anyone know how to fix either of these? The first problem is 10000x more important.
btw 317[pi]
